</div>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<math>[ u ]_{H^{1/2} (\mathbf{T}^{2})}^{2} = \sum_{k \in \mathbf{Z}^{2}} | k | \big| \hat{u} (k) \big|^{2} < + \infty:</math>
</div>

